2.18. Power of attorney
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Your card, PIN code and MasterCard SecureCode are only for your own
personal use.
.sp 3mm
If you wish to grant another person power of attorney to use your card
to make withdrawals from your account, this person is to have his/her
own card, his/her own PIN code and his/her own MasterCard SecureCode. The
person's use of the card is subject to the same regulations
as apply to you.
.sp 3mm
If you no longer wish this person to be able to make withdrawals from the
account, you must ensure that thep physical card is returned to &BANKNAVN.,
and MasterCard on mobile phone must be deleted together
with a written statement from you revoking the power of attorney.
.sp 3mm
