2.15. Faults and defects in the service etc.
:SKRSLUT.
.br
&BANKNAVN. accepts no liability for a payment recipient refusing to
accept the card as a means of payment. Any claims concerning faults and
defects in the services delivered are to be addressed to the payment
recipient - however, see Article 2.6 concerning purchases via the
Internet.
