2.16 Termination of the card/card account
:SKRSLUT.
.br
&BANKNAVN. may terminate the present agreement on two months' notice
except in the event of material breach of contract, Company Cards
without notice, though,
see Article 2.17. In the event of termination, you will receive a
refund of a proportional amount of any fees you may have paid in
advance for the use of the card.
