2.12. Change of name or address, and termination of use of card
:SKRSLUT.
.br
If you/the company changes your/the company's name and no longer wish
to use the card, you/the company must inform &BANKNAVN. of this in
writing without delay. You must also cut the physical card into pieces and
return it to &BANKNAVN.. &BANKNAVN. must be informed immediately and in
writing if you/the company change your/the company's address.
.sp 3mm
